questions.title: A list of all possible launch commands for zeronet.conf
questions.body:
This is what I have accumulated so far but I know there are more.
```
trackers_proxy = tor
tor_use_bridges = 
tor = always
fileserver_port = 35060
optional_limit = 100%

autodownload_bigfile_size_limit 15
ui_password PASSWORD
ui_ip "*"
homepage /address
force_encryption
```
